item.title: How can I open a class file? Specifically JFrame.class
item.dc:creator: @chassy13 Chassy13
item.description:
@chassy13 wrote:

The person who created the client may have deleted the java files to prevent leeching or unwanted changes…if this is the case then you will need to use a java decompiler to decompile the file, change it, and then recompile it.
